digest Parameters

When you define a digest transformation, you set the action attribute to digest and specify the parameters.

PARAMETER	REQUIRED?	VALUE
connectionName	Yes	Name of the connection used to sync the data.
object	Yes	The connected object that you want to extract data from.
fields	Yes	An array of names of the fields that you want to extract.
